<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> وَاسْتَيْقَنَتْهاا أَنْفُسُهُمْ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وقال:</span> إِنْ نَظُنُّ إِلّاا ظَنًّا وَماا نَحْنُ بِمُسْتَيْقِنِينَ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
